tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Green_Transportation_Impact (
  city VARCHAR,
  country VARCHAR,
  initiative_name VARCHAR,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  air_quality_index INT,
  public_health_outcomes VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE Green_Transportation_Initiatives (
    initiative_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_name TEXT,
    initiative_description TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Air_Quality_Data (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_id INT,
    pollutant TEXT,
    level FLOAT,
    measurement_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (initiative_id) REFERENCES Green_Transportation_Initiatives(initiative_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Public_Health_Outcomes (
    outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_id INT,
    condition TEXT,
    impact VARCHAR,
    assessment_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (initiative_id) REFERENCES Green_Transportation_Initiatives(initiative_id)
);

CREATE TABLE GreenInitiativesImpact (
  initiative_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  initiative_name VARCHAR(255),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  impact_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE AirQualityData (
  data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  date_recorded DATE,
  pollutant_type VARCHAR(50),
  pollutant_level FLOAT,
  location VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE PublicHealthOutcomes (
  outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  outcome_name VARCHAR(100),
  outcome_description TEXT,
  affected_population INT,
  outcome_rating FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE InitiativesHealthImpact (
  impact_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  initiative_id INT,
  outcome_id INT,
  impact_date DATE,
  impact_details TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE AirQualityData (
  data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  location_id INT,
  date DATE,
  pm25_level DECIMAL,
  pm10_level DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE HealthOutcomes (
  outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  location_id INT,
  date DATE,
  disease_type VARCHAR(50),
  affected_population INT
);

CREATE TABLE InitiativesImpact (
  impact_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  initiative_id INT,
  location_id INT,
  impact_factor DECIMAL,
  impact_description TEXT
);
